{"tid":996060,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"女童告父強姦庭上突推翻證供 一男兩女被控妨礙司法公正","createTime":"2019-01-26T03:26:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-26T08:11:29.000Z","uid":211744,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"218f6995b7dee35c4114dc1df0407da650fbef7c","tid":996060,"uid":211744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T03:26:20.000Z","msg":"巴士司機被指多次在寓所內非禮兼強姦親女，首次案發時女兒年僅11歲。不過，女兒早前在庭上突然推翻口供，聲稱父親不讓她玩新手機以及「錫細佬唔錫我」，因而誣告父親，法官前日指導陪審團裁定涉案司機強姦等罪名不成立。警方同晚拘捕一男兩女，控以串謀妨礙司法公正罪，案件今在屯門裁判法院提堂。<br />\n<br />\n控方以不同英文字母作為三名被告的簡稱，男被告現年42歲，兩名女被告則分別40歲及65歲。三人涉於去年10月20日至本月16日間，威嚇女童X在庭上作假口供。裁判官頒下命令，嚴禁傳媒報道X的姓名、住址、職業，以及X與各被告的關係。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，男被告趁40歲女被告探監時，要求她在強姦案開審前帶X回內地，她亦照做，而65歲女被告則要求X與辯方律師合作，否則會「冇咗個老竇」。三名被告暫時毋須答辯，押後至今年3月8日再訊，以待警方繼續調查及諮詢律政司意見。三人不准保釋，還柙監房候訊。<br />\n<br />\n【案件編號:TMCC230/19】<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190125/59184848\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190125%2F59184848&d=UwQMSjbS41QxOfoXNLYtBb%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=f8483a06\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190125%2F59184848&h=124e21f7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190125/59184848</a>"},{"pid":"99cf279d62b423b88a47f35b470abd3170d40265","tid":996060,"uid":54431,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T03:27:27.000Z","msg":"好睇過電視劇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23fab7a44e96c4e2253242f4e46363dcbaa7e4d5","tid":996060,"uid":211744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T03:27:36.000Z","msg":"個阿嫲同姑姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3a070dd3d11229a37a706c99b1d776e56143483","tid":996060,"uid":53672,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T03:32:31.000Z","msg":"拉哂全屋入去過年就岩，搞自己個女既畜生都幫"},{"pid":"f7e3b678a4597521578cb659c9b6846792fc7e4f","tid":996060,"uid":7547,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T03:36:00.000Z","msg":"唔係跟車太貼咁簡單 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  全部炒嗮"},{"pid":"45bc6f3b1efb39a78ab7ac60ff0a75095431668f","tid":996060,"uid":211744,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d3a070dd3d11229a37a706c99b1d776e56143483","tid":996060,"uid":53672,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T03:32:31.000Z","msg":"拉哂全屋入去過年就岩，搞自己個女既畜生都幫"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T07:10:04.000Z","msg":"我寧願係個細路女講大話屈人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n戀童都算 仲要搞自己個女<br />\n個阿嫲同姑姐都唔撚係人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f82ef91a728e54795218a07c0b9bdc401c97fa6","tid":996060,"uid":53238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T08:07:44.000Z","msg":"威脅無左老豆都 work ?<br />\n無左仲好 wo"},{"pid":"12a030926d598eab2aa9e7e1ad1788dacb6eeb4b","tid":996060,"uid":35014,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T08:11:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"11555f5bbcab7f3fe88e42c2b74863a19aad2a13","tid":996060,"uid":149035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T08:11:29.000Z","msg":"反轉"}]}